Text:
Someone called edna2 has posted a link on my cross post on Demonoid to a French version of the Stockholm sprints:
www[dot]demonoid[dot]com/files/details/2176351/

Wow, thanks! That's great! Since I do speak French it would be fun to listen to French commentators. :)

But my all-time favorites are David Goldstrom and Mike Dixon. So I keep my fingers crossed that you are able to upload all the remaining races of this most exciting season!
